{"type":null,"faqId":22389,"title":"华为盒子和荣耀盒子有什么区别？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀盒子（M321）专注影视播放，小巧时尚，内容丰富，画质出众，是一款性价比极高的网络电视机顶盒；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>华为盒子（M330）镜面高端精致，接口齐备，影音、游戏随心畅享，是构建无线家庭影院的首选。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、华为盒子顶面有闪亮平整的装饰镜片，采用精致的点纹和镜面银LOGO点缀，带有铝合金光泽（钛灰色）的中框涂层，金属质感的亮边处理；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、华为盒子具有蓝牙4.0功能，不仅能看电视， 还可以提供更多的家庭娱乐功能</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1)盒子内预置“游戏中心”，可以外接蓝牙手柄，在大电视上玩游戏；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2)外接蓝牙音箱、耳机，构建无线家庭影院；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3)使用蓝牙遥控器（需额外购买），可以360度无死角遥控。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、华为盒子有 STB in 接口，可以连接传统数字电视内容（如高清机顶盒），在华为盒子和传统机顶盒之前更便捷切换画面。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":241,"faqType":"功能概览","useful":11,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6269","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Know-Product","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628512000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":1730,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"M330,MediaQ M330,华为盒子,M321,荣耀盒子,区别","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}